reviewText:
This is a great series that is wholesome and fun! This Happy Mother's Day DVD has the following episodes:
1- The Giddy Grandma
2- Mama's New Job
3- Week at Grandma's
4- Lend a Helping Hand
5- Think of Those in Need
This was a great set of Berenstain Bears episodes. The kids loved them and it kept them entertained the whole time. I think it's great for kids up to 8 or 9 years old.
